  "title": "Order Processing Administrator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Order Processing Administrator (German MNC/Benoi Area)</strong><br /><br /><br /><strong>Working Hours</strong>: Mon to Fri, 8.30 am to 5.30 pm</p><p><strong>Job Incentives Structure</strong></p><ul><li>Basic salary (Up to $3000; commensurate with experience)</li><li>Work life balance </li><li>Annual bonus</li><li>Comprehensive insurance coverage </li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><p>The position is designed for an Administrator (order processing) to support Sales Team, reporting to the Sales Manager. <br />The job includes preparing quotation, order, sales order, delivery note. It requires cooperation and communication with customers and head office in Europe.</p><p><strong>The successful candidate would preferably have:</strong></p><ul><li>Nitec & above</li><li>Candidates with little or no experience will also be considered. Training will be provided</li><li>MS Office competent  </li><li>SAP knowledge is an advantage     </li></ul>",
